<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Capturing_User_Input">Capturing User Input</span></h3>
<h4><span class="mw-headline" id="Key_Presses">Key Presses</span></h4>
<p>I check if the user presses the ESC key to cancel out of Edit Text Mode, restoring input to the main Game Viewport
</p>
